    "description": "耐心牌》将类似于纸牌游戏的玩法与RPG和roguelite元素相结合。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/48983964fa067ad791c1c37671d37289.poster.avif?t=1643140425\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/48983964fa067ad791c1c37671d37289.webm?t=1643140425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/48983964fa067ad791c1c37671d37289.mp4?t=1643140425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>选择你的英雄，通过摧毁他们所有的卡片来对抗各种敌人。<br>使用不同级别的法术，用强大的物品和药水装备自己，使你的战斗更容易。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/327a3896ace8847a3603f337238da211.poster.avif?t=1643140425\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/327a3896ace8847a3603f337238da211.webm?t=1643140425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/327a3896ace8847a3603f337238da211.mp4?t=1643140425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每次运行都是不同的，但死亡并不是终点。<br>通过每次胜利获得强大的钻石球，可以解锁永久升级甚至是新的英雄。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/0c51ca2187a6bc663e6cb709ed1dd45c.poster.avif?t=1643140425\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/0c51ca2187a6bc663e6cb709ed1dd45c.webm?t=1643140425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/0c51ca2187a6bc663e6cb709ed1dd45c.mp4?t=1643140425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>主要特点：</strong><br>- 基于回合制的卡牌对战<br>- 不同的英雄有不同的天赋树<br>- 各种物品和药水<br>- 随机生成<br>- 通过永久升级的Roguelite<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/4df46e2e0a3096bd266293a325763a47.poster.avif?t=1643140425\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/4df46e2e0a3096bd266293a325763a47.webm?t=1643140425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693660/extras/4df46e2e0a3096bd266293a325763a47.mp4?t=1643140425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
